properties.areaDesc: Grand Marais to Taconite Harbor MN; Grand Portage to Grand Marais MN
properties.headline: Gale Warning issued January 8 at 3:07AM CST until January 8 at 10:00AM CST by NWS Duluth MN
properties.description:
* WHAT...North winds 10 to 15 knots with gusts up to 35 knots and
waves 2 feet or less.

* WHERE...Grand Portage to Grand Marais MN and Grand Marais to
Taconite Harbor MN.

* WHEN...Until 10 AM CST this morning.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous waves which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING IN EFFECT UNTIL 10 AM CST THIS MORNING
